data.description: BETTER THAN NEW, completely renovated 4-side brick with siding accents at oversized carport and covered porch.  This gorgeous open floor plan features 3 spacious bedrooms, a large rear yard, a luxury kitchen with a breakfast bar and eat-in area, and exquisite granite tops.  An abundance of parking makes this home a no-brainer.       New systems in the home include a water heater, electrical wiring, much of the plumbing, and an HVAC system.  This home was modernized by converting the sectioned-off common area rooms into a stunning open space.  You can not get all of this in new construction for this price.   New plumbing fixtures, lights, appliances, cabinets, vanities, waterproof luxury vinyl plank flooring, luxury level granite in the kitchen, tiled flooring, and shower surrounds with a niche in the hall and primary bath.  Flush mount lighting and two ceiling fans are installed in the open space.       This home has it all, with room to grow on a large unfinished basement.  A French drain system has been installed around the sides and rear so you can finish the basement without worries about water. This home ranks at the top of the list for space, modernization, functionality, versatility, construction, lot space, and price.  No HOA means your house is your house…No nosy neighbors in your business.  Act fast.  This is a keeper.  Ask How the seller's preferred lender can get qualified buyers $7500 in down payment assistance!  Listing agent and Seller are related
